Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you'll be sleeping over at school tonight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The karate championship is drawing\Nnear, so everyone's pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there's no school tomorrow, we\Ndecided to stay over night and practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just got permission from our teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:28.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about our dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry I could collapse any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just go to Poirot downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get your breakfast there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be back at noon tomorrow,\Nso take care of Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said to eat at Poirot for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll be having boxed meals\Nfrom a convenience store tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because today, Poirot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:07.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,We will be closed\Non the 4th and 5th\Nfor personal reasons.\NPoirot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Poirot's owner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did say he'd invited the neighborhood\Nassociation guys to a hot spring trip today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know, there's that Iroha Sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,Closed today\NIroha Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they're closed too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he invited a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there are a lot of shops with their lights off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, every single eatery in the neighborhood is blacked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it is, there won't be food delivery too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case, I brought the flyers from all kinds\Nof eating places that were in our mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we try them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything that looks good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Specialty Pizza "Colosseo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miso cutlet "Tsubouchi"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hiroshima-style okonomiyaki "Kondou"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of which I'm in the mood for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a distance, but why don't we give this a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I Love You Miss Mystery - the one now in an endless labyrinth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's embrace this love and solve puzzle right now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If all cases were men...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose the invisible mysteries would be women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At a somewhat nostalgic ramen shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The smell of a case reerks to high heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:14.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:14.92,Signs,,0,0,0,,RAMEN SO GOOD IT'S TO DIE FOR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.21,Signs,,0,0,0,,So Good It's To Die For â€”\hRamen Ogura
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's quite a venerable shop, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture on the flyer was a lot nicer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we look for another shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This kind of unvarnished shop is what we call a "hidden gem"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be super tasty and well-loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus on a cold day like this it's best\Nto eat some ramen and warm up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it all to hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess you have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, c'mon in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chilly today, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And no other customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anywhere but that seat please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the seat of one of our loyal customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:25.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, although he was a loyal customer, he passed away last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:27.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Ogura Katsumasa (49)\N"Ramen Ogura" Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just my desire to reserve that seat in memory\Nof him until the 49 days of mourning are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry 'bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why flowers have been left on the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two, even?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I won our bet then, Sayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:53.72,Signs,,0,0,0,,Oohashi Sayo (28)\NPart-time Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My part-time pay is low enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut me loose once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, give our guests some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of bet were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether the number of guests today\Nwould go into double digits or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner time's almost over, and we just finally\Nhelped them make it ten customers on the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I take your orders please?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any recommendations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your best bet is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our pride and joy that's so delicious it's to die for:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THE DEATH LORD RAMEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We do have the plain o' miso or dipping\Nramen on the menu just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you somehow want anything other than...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THE DEATH LORD RAMEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll still serve you as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll try some of that Death Lord ramen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two orders of the Death Lord ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:55.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing we chose ramen like Uncle suggested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scumbag, what the hell're you doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't serve ramen to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what's with using that manner of speech to a customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made a special effort to come to this\Nseedy shop where business is so slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:19.39,Signs,,0,0,0,,Saizu Tokumori (51)\NReal Estate Company President
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just to give you fine folks some\Nmuch needed profit, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're losing customers only because those young jackasses\Nfrom your place are always causing trouble in my shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad, they're all brainless, energetic grunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we should've already properly compensated\Nyou for the tableware my boys broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I did give those boys an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telling them they should've made sure to\Nseriously hurt the owner while they're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm joking, joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hat seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.77,0:08:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knocked it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wipe it for me, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who spilled it, so wipe it up yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, what an insolent shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for putting out shabby\Nflowers as decoration in a spot like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your order!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not ordering anything, please go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have that "so good it's to die for" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you made up your mind yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,General?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you ask me, I won't sell this shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we and the Haido Shopping Street proprietors have\Njoined forces and made an unwavering pact recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I great example of "ignorance is bliss".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your own shop is being called the black sheep, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I came in here, I got a haircut from\NCut House Taninaka next door, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The owner of that barbershop was complaining too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was saying he'd -like for this beat up ramen shop to be\Nrun out of this stylish shopping street since it just didn't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that for real!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, spewing nonsense, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only said, "If he remodeled once in a while,\Nhis business would've been more prosperous."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My shop and yours opened on this shopping\Nstreet at the same time twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:36.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Taninaka Atsushi (47)\NBarbershop Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My shop has remodeled three times already,\Nyet this place has been the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about doing it,\Nbut things are a bit tight over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instigating a falling out between friends in order to wreck\Nthis shopping district was Mr. Land Shark's aim all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have the Death Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:02.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Death Lord ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bamboo shoots are piled sky high!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a pun on "Death Lord" and "bamboo shoots".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,enma
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:21.41,Signs,,0,0,0,,menma
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the chopsticks are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey mister, could you pass those chopsticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get right to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's... eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YUM-MY!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never tasted anything like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These bamboo shoots are especially delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secret to its tastiness is in those bamboo shoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The recipe-is a trade secret, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could get used to this flavor all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should invite Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, the\Nprofessor, and the others here next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A run-down shop with a top-notch taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it won't be closing down anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cheap, fast, and tasty is our motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're definitely gonna keep on truckin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In contrast, my company is going down in flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes me feel as if I want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you fold up your fishy business...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And start a new trade instead!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy to make it in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, you're left-handed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, earlier you wiped up the water\Non the table using your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was corrected by my parents when\NI was a kid, so I'm ambidextrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I still use my left hand whenever\NI eat, or else I feel uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ramen so good it's to die for", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only someone could die after eating this for my sake,\Nthen this shop would go out of business immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try poisoning this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been listening this whole time, but you're\Njust spewing bullshit and being disrespectful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's take it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a piece of my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.16,0:13:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think we're gonna fall for that same trick again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know this guy's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bet he's just faking a collapse in my shop to raise\N1 a big fuss about having gotten food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taninaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll throw this bastard out onto the street and wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN'T TOUCH HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be best if everyone returned to where they\Noriginally were without touching anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, in addition to the ambulance, call the police as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ramen so good it's to die for", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:15:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And immediately after eating it, he\Ncollapsed in agony and passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the ramen certainly was good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought he'd really die for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People don't just drop dead from food that's too delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the victim's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizu Tokumori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 51 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was apparently the president of the real\Nestate business he managed in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he had wanted to buy up and raze the entire Haido\NShopping Street, and build a large shopping mall instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people of this area considered shim to be a major nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was considered a nuisance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to destroy this shopping street...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears that he would frequently use his\Nemployees to purposely disrupt the businesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When they came here, they'd find some reason to\Npick on one of our customers and start a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't even count how many of my ramen bowls they've broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the same at your shop, wasn't it, Taninaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Purposely shifting while getting a shave\Nand causing their cheeks to get cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then raising a huge fuss and demanding\Nwe pay for the medical billâ€”it's their routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did it go today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said he had gone to your shop to get a\Nhaircut before coming here to eat ramen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, today it went fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:28.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this guy was a so-called land shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the whole shopping street got together and\Nplanned to file a lawsuit over his outrageous behavior, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attorney representing them died\Nlast month, and the lawsuit was dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could say he was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because my dad was trying to stop a fight here while eating his\Nramen, and a heart a tack struck him due to his chronic disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was taken to the hospital and died there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "dad", you mean you're the attorney's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:05.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From when she was little, that attorney\Nwould often bring her along to this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used to say she'd also open a ramen shop once she grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never thought she'd really come and\Nask me for any job, even a part time one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, what was your dad's chronic disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hypertension!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His death of cerebral hemorrhage was probably due to\Nhis over-agitation from getting dragged into the fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctor said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it bad for people with high blood pressure to eat ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father took medicine to control his blood pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was even told by his doctor that it was OK\Nto eat ramen as long as he didn't drink the soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim's cause of death was poison, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the coroner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably ingested the hydrocyanic poison\Nthrough his mouth as he was eating ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So in short, having been in this shop at the time of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And possessing sufficient motive, the three of you\Nhad the opportunity to poison the victim to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there was poison in our ramen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shall investigate that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you all would submit to body searches, and wait\Noutside until we finish our investigation inside the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it wise to restrict it to only the three of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That customer grabbed him by the collar, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking I'd give him a good\Ntalking to, since he was talking bull...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll undergo a body search too, and then GET OUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, on such a cold day, why did I have to be shut out too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how ramen is made?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask the expert for that sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had laced poison somewhere during the\Ncooking process, there's no way he'd answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I usually see on TV is to boil the noodles\Nupon receiving an order from the customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then add the sauce and stuff\Nlike seasoning in the ramen bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, after that, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd put soup into the bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you drain the noodles and put them into the bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then finish it off with garnishes such as roast\Npork, eggs, bamboo shoots, and green onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in the case of my shop, Sayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nis the one who does the garnishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, if it had been you or Sayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either one of you could have laced it\Nwith poison at your leisure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that'd be the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we never laced anything with poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damned straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, say, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you eat ramen with the late Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} often?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} really likes that he'd\Ndefinitely eat up before he even touched the noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like bamboo shoots or eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never actually looked at how he ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what about any habits he has when he eats ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Habits?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, I was thinking if he always touches something out\Nof habit, it'd be easy to just apply the poison there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you were the only one, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person who didn't get close\Nto Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} nor Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you guys were sitting in the seats between me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and if I recall, the closest you ever got to Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was when you held out the chopstick stand to us, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't use those chopsticks at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:19.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I wonder why we didn't have any\Nchopsticks in the stand in front of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because there was a customer who dropped that\Nstand, and scattered the chopsticks all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And before I could refill it with some\Nreplacement chopsticks, you guys came.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unsurprisingly, the customer was one of Saizu's subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We made sure to charge him for the chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, is refilling the chopsticks your duty, Sayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me all right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never touched the chopsticks that man used.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.88,0:21:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since that seat was my dad's reserved seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There weren't really any customers who sat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means the loyal customer\Nwho died last month was indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was that attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sat in that seat without taking no\Nfor an answer, does he always do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he found out it was the lawyer's seat, he'd\Npurposely sit there as a form of harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sitting at that seat was something\Nthat could've been foreseen to some extent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.29,0:22:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among those three who were in the shop at that\Ntime and had the chance to poison Saizu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who on earth did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A poisoning trick beyond our expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall clear up our cloudy field of vision and expose the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART TWO)
