Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.53,0:24:28.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.26,0:24:33.05,Signs,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Signs}-kun{\r}, you look\Nexactly like little\NShinichi when you\Ntake off your glasses!
